%section.project
  %article
    %figure.subnav
      %a.ion-home.wow.zoomIn{href: "/"}
      %a.ion-chevron-left.wow.zoomIn{href: "/work/bistro23"}
      %a.ion-chevron-right.wow.zoomIn{href: "/work/browndog"}
    %figure.intro
      .item-text.wow.fadeInLeft
        %h2 Rumble
        %h5 Location Based Chat App (Student Project)
        %p Ru.wow.fadeInRightmble is a geo-locational chat app which is ideal for large conferences and sporting events. After signing in and setting the radius of your search, you are able to select a feed to chat in or create you own. The concept is based around the fact that thunder can be heard only within the radius of a certain location.
      .item-image.wow.fadeInUp
        = image_tag("work/rumble-devices.png")
    %figure.phone
      .item-image.wow.fadeInUp
        = image_tag("work/rumble-1.png")
      .item-text.wow.fadeInRight
        %h3 Loading...
        %p Intro screen while app opens.
    %figure.phone
      .item-image.wow.fadeInUp
        = image_tag("work/rumble-2.png")
      .item-text.wow.fadeInRight
        %h3 Login
        %p Login to the app to begin use, or create a new account.
    %figure.phone
      .item-image.wow.fadeInUp
        = image_tag("work/rumble-3.png")
      .item-text.wow.fadeInRight
        %h3 Select a Radius
        %p To determine who you will be able to chat with, select a radius of the distance you want included.
    %figure.phone
      .item-image.wow.fadeInUp
        = image_tag("work/rumble-4.png")
      .item-text.wow.fadeInRight
        %h3 Available Feeds
        %p Based on your selected radius, the available feeds are shown. If there isn't one on the subject you want, create your own!
    %figure.phone
      .item-image.wow.fadeInUp
        = image_tag("work/rumble-5.png")
      .item-text.wow.fadeInRight
        %h3 Feed Description
        %p After you select a feed, you are brought to a screen which provides details on what it's about.
    %figure.phone
      .item-image.wow.fadeInUp
        = image_tag("work/rumble-6.png")
      .item-text.wow.fadeInRight
        %h3 Chat Screen
        %p Have a conversation with the other users in the feed!
